            bindings = <
        &kp INSERT    &kp N1  &kp N2  &kp N3  &kp MINUS  &kp HOME  &kp PG_DN  &kp PG_UP  &kp END    &kp COLON
        &kp DELETE    &kp N4  &kp N5  &kp N6  &kp DOT    &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN   &kp UP     &kp RIGHT  &kp SEMICOLON
&trans  &kp CAPSLOCK  &kp N7  &kp N8  &kp N9  &kp N0     &none     &kp RGUI   &kp RALT   &kp RCTRL  &kp RSHFT      &trans
                              &trans  &mo 3   &kp ESC    &trans    &trans     &trans
